sub_title: CEO at Comm-Co, Atexshop.com, Ruggedshop.nl and Ecommshop.com. Feel free to browse!
summary:
Welcome to my LinkedIn page! My name is Jacques Duerinck and I am an entrepreneur in sales. With over 20 years of experience, I have been working with customers all over the world, in more than 70 countries. My focus is on Technical Sales in software and presales and project management.

Throughout my career, I have developed a passion for Communications and Innovations in intrinsically safe products, Atex and IECEx. My expertise also includes Distribution of rugged products and special projects over the globe. As a result, I have built a large Atex fashion distribution network, including popular websites like www.atexshop.com and ruggedshop.nl, and www.comm-co.com.

I am proud to have worked with some of the biggest names in the industry, including Shell, Aramco, Nam, and Exxon Mobile. It is my belief that a key component to success in any industry is to be creative and have fun while doing it.

One of my passions is app development  for Atex and IECEx products , and I have had the opportunity to work on many special projects on a global level. My expertise in Atex and IECEx  has allowed me to help many businesses improve their projects  and increasing their revenue.

If you're looking for a professional with a passion for innovation, technical sales, and project management, look no further. With my expertise, creativity, and extensive experience, I can help take your business to the next level. Connect with me today to see how we can work together.
